ClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=3d105d0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%89%E9%B6%B4-per-day-or-today%2F&h=4f9d00be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/緊張的劉鶴-per-day-or-today/</a><br />\n5 million tons per day<br />\n分分鐘係心底話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b65d219dc0dc5f3f3eadb7daef276bbbdb77339","tid":1821123,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"786c1e75b1f58a93c581f400cc6d739760803f5d","tid":1821123,"uid":14494,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"王子復仇記撞正港英女間諜<br />\n<br />\n好浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc3701148d7c3198bd4c04f1bbb8f8b673a27db","tid":1821123,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"手足好波"},{"pid":"48ec21d2fd1b6eb8cfb60e94b1ae87f1981fe939","tid":1821123,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:18:53.000Z","msg":"借個位宣傳吸引火力黎推post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfor 想健康升級/心態體力提升手足參考<br />\n<br />\n入黎補補正能量調整心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人夠正能量先頂到落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自衞隊身體質素＆勇氣全世界都大有必要<br />\n香港人 only you can change yourself<br />\n未來嘅希望由我地做起<br />\n<br />\nStep 10.心存希望 管理情緒<br />\nHeal yourself🌱<br />\nFree yourself 🈵<br />\nFree the emotion🎉<br />\n無論咩時間 心存希望<br />\n我的使命係帶希望比大家<br />\n我地一齊行落去 <br />\n沒有處理不到的事<br />\n只有處理不到的心情<br />\n管理好情緒 有助我地做得更好<br />\n⚡️減少重複接觸影響自己的負面人事<br />\n🍎每日練習 突破舒適圈 比自己進步一下<br />\n🔥要增肌/提神/搵工/調理身體想心情更好歡迎黎搵我運動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\n啱嘅就聽下幫自己再幫人<br />\n 唔啱聽我都唔會覆你 <br />\n重點係大家Build up自信＋能耐做更強嘅自己 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">We can do it</span></span> <br />\n香港人團結 正能量<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地要內在夠強 大返佢地<br />\n<br />\n永續健康身心 成功致勝<br />\n營養/心態歡迎搵我幫手<br />\n教完大家要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTG ME幫你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動打仗飲食法<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n支持升級黃圈 培訓人才人人出資資助小朋友就業<br />\n免費簡單健康分析<br />\n收費嘅跟進我都做 <br />\n支持黃圈返正價出錢幫人<br />\nNothing is free for granted <br />\nIf you Learn, do help more ppl<br />\n得閒係屋企/搵我做下運動放鬆<br />\nBuild up 自己自信 無狗敢搞你<br />\n如果你期望唔出付就會有結果<br />\n請你離開<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=cb9d8a60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=1d28f868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice</a><br />\n討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/THHATalk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTHHATalk&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=0aaa5115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/THHATalk</a><br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗白色恐怖 <br />\n反共抗中 我地勢不兩立<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\nUnited, We can win the fight"},{"pid":"f4b971b59c0150c2629bcd96740acbf14177ce0a","tid":1821123,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"小學生沒讀過書都咁聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b4fed14f0d6bdb10a301c5bef7993d00e7d7d2","tid":1821123,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b9ea647828a8f983ecd01029401b863d15ceab","tid":1821123,"uid":303680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4b971b59c0150c2629bcd96740acbf14177ce0a","tid":1821123,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"小學生沒讀過書都咁聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"唔止嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得呢條友係冇乜人性同下限先上到呢個位"},{"pid":"ed61619f34b7f856de63323a856ae3d59790b9a0","tid":1821123,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=595df811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"bec7dd937704a18f495af48ef1c5c68f49e83234","tid":1821123,"uid":40226,"like":4,"dislike":0,